::Prowl::

Prowl reaches Iron Raptor's quarters, the doors opening as he walks up to 
them.

He looks around as he enters. This was the first time he'd been here. Prowl 
walks to the bed, gently placing Iron Raptor on it.

He stops halfway through covering her with a blanket, looking down at her 
face. She was beautiful, he thinks to himself as he puts the blanket up to 
her chin and turns around to leave for the meeting.

Prowl stops at the door as a thought occurrs to him. Maybe he should stay 
with her ... to make sure she was ok. He turns around. That was probably a 
good idea.

Prowl walks to a chair, moves it to near Iron Raptor's bed, and sits down.
